release.name: Version 2.1.31
release.body:
This is version 2.1.31 of the unfoldingWord® Hebrew Bible. Download the TSV source below and see the README file for more information about the project.

Note that you can see this resource on Door43, tC Create, gatewayEdit, or in translationCore.

This version has a few small fixes to a few books. This release makes edits to the following books: SNG and ISA.

[Click here](https://git.door43.org/unfoldingWord/hbo_uhb/compare/v2.1.30...v2.1.31) for changes between v2.1.30 and v2.1.31.
